<h4 id="50">1.1.3. Checking the result</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Open the variation in your plentyShop and make sure the settings match your needs.
Modify the settings further as needed.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the widget <a href="/en/online-store/shop-builder#_order_properties">Order properties</a> to display order properties in the plentyShop.
