Modify the settings further as needed.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the widget <a href="/en/online-store/shop-builder#_order_properties">Order properties</a> to display order characteristics in the plentyShop.
In the widget settings, you can control e.g. the colour and spacing of the order characteristics.</p>
